00:12:51,504 --> 00:12:52,772
Then three years ago,
she suddenly

273
00:12:52,805 --> 00:12:54,173
turned into a whole new person.

274
00:12:54,207 --> 00:12:56,042
She and her mother
became best friends,

275
00:12:56,075 --> 00:12:58,411
I thought maybe she had
a boyfriend or was going through

276
